Ugustan n hipun niɣd {{Talatinit|Aurelius Augustinus}} niɣd {{Tafransist|Saint Augustin}}. Iga yan ɣ ifulusfn imaziɣ iɣatarn. ilul ɣ tama n taɣast ɣ tamzɣa (ɣil suq ahras ɣ tamurt n Dzyr) as n 13 novembre 354 {{Asggas amaziɣ| as nwis 31 ktubr 1304}} ittumḍal ɣ 28 ɣuct 430 ɣ Hipun (ɣil Σannaba ɣ Dzayr). Ayt dars gan kullu imaziɣn mac ar ttinin masd ibbas itfr irumiyn niɣd (Afrikkic arumi), innas uhu (Tafrikkict ilillin). Ar ittara s talati nit ig yan ɣ Kkuẓ iɣatarn n tmzgida Tarumit ɣ ussan ns imzwura.  Iɣatarn ad lli igan Agrram arumi {{Tafransist|Saint}} Ugustan, Agrram Umbrwas , Agrram Jirum {{Tafransist|Saint Jérôme}}, Agrram Grigwar amzwaru {{Tafransist|Grégoire Ier}} d 33 ṭalb n tmzgida tarumit. Ikatulikiyn ar bdda skarn tafuɣla n tamṭṭalt ns graygat as n 28 ɣuct (15 ɣuct amaziɣ). Ait uɣtuduks nttnin  aras skar n tafuɣla as n 15 yulyu (2 ɣuct amaziɣ).
